# Vercel access token for deploying the hosted WoodSmith project.
# Create it in the Vercel dashboard (logged in as the account/team that owns
# `woodsmith`): Account Settings -> Tokens -> Create Token.
#
# Copy this file to  .vercel-token.local  and paste the token below.
# The real file matches *.local in .gitignore, so it is never committed.
# Used by scripts/deploy.ps1.
VERCEL_TOKEN=

# Optional: the team slug, required only if `woodsmith` lives under a team
# (it does — team_4AgM6HjzfR3pE38elkRNfqgP). Find the slug in the team's
# Vercel dashboard URL, e.g. vercel.com/<team-slug>.
VERCEL_SCOPE=
